products.title: Hampton White - Translucent Pleated Skylight Blind
products.description: Their pleated hampton range, comes in light neutral shades. Perfect for sprucing up your loft or conservatory without the light loss from blackout fabric. A screen fabric, this faric is great for getting some uv protection without sacrificing natural light. Product id: db-pls0113 fabric colour: white material: 100% polyester headrail: white rails and hardware with pull down tab and visible guide wires to support the blind fabric.
